com.googlecode.memcachefy.interceptor

Class CacheInterceptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.memcachefy.interceptor.CacheInterceptor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CacheProxy, Ejb3CacheInterceptor

    public abstract class CacheInterceptor
extends Object
    The intercetor is intended to be used by extending it with concrete implementations of dynamic proxies (reflection API) or EJB3 interceptors. Once we have a method intercepted CacheInterceptor will change its default behaviour by caching objects returned by it. A hash key based on the parameters of the calling method will be used as the key of the cache entry.
    Author:
    bhlangonijr
